/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b20a0c312244900fe5adecd26eb9a44cd7bdd7f","tid":343774,"uid":16565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T17:59:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整張好多相，好多野彈出黎個啲卡</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 但男仔會唔會冇乜感覺收到都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又啱，睇你男友係咩類型。比較直嘅就送佢想要嘅野可能仲好（Game 呀鞋呀）</blockquote><br />\n我有聽過男朋友讚過有個女仔寫左封好長嘅信俾佢男朋友所以覺得個女仔好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢又唔太會睇相 因為我平時sd我地嘅情侶相俾佢個陣有時會叫我唔洗sd俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我又送過好多買嘅野 反而親手做嘅小禮物未送過 所以想送下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就新手整啦，再寫長嘅信。今次就打感動"},{"pid":"b82b65cf891583e5be9f33c9b5cc77e371404fdd","tid":343774,"uid":16565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:00:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>整張好多相，好多野彈出黎個啲卡</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 但男仔會唔會冇乜感覺收到都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你又啱，睇你男友係咩類型。比較直嘅就送佢想要嘅野可能仲好（Game 呀鞋呀）</blockquote><br />\n我有聽過男朋友讚過有個女仔寫左封好長嘅信俾佢男朋友所以覺得個女仔好好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但佢又唔太會睇相 因為我平時sd我地嘅情侶相俾佢個陣有時會叫我唔洗sd俾佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但我又送過好多買嘅野 反而親手做嘅小禮物未送過 所以想送下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n咁就新手整啦，再寫長嘅信。今次就打感動</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">親</span>"},{"pid":"042564dd3e046ae250ad0b53edc8ae31e16f9a8d","tid":343774,"uid":828,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-01T18:00:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>整張好多相，好多野彈出黎個啲卡</blockquote><br />\n有諗過 但男仔會唔會冇乜感覺收到都<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gi